{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"क्या तेरे पास ढाँपने लेने वाली (क़ियामत) की ख़बर पहुँची?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-ghāshiyati ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) news","(of) the Overwhelming","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-ghāshiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1200],[3,1200,2050],[4,2050,3925]]}},{"name":"88:2","price":"उस दिन कई चेहरे अपमानित होंगे।","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) humbled","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,3160],[3,3160,4965]]}},{"name":"88:3","price":"कठिन परिश्रम करने वाले, थक जाने वाले।","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿāmilatun nāṣibatun ","translations":["Laboring","exhausted","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿāmilatun","nāṣibatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1210],[2,1210,3985]]}},{"name":"88:4","price":"वे गर्म धधकती आग में प्रवेश करेंगे।","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"taṣlā nāran ḥāmiyatan ","translations":["They will burn","(in) a Fire","intensely hot","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taṣlā","nāran","ḥāmiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1630],[3,1630,3355]]}},{"name":"88:5","price":"उन्हें खौलते सोते का जल पिलाया जाएगा।","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"tus'qā min ʿaynin āniyatin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","from","a spring","boiling","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["tus'qā","min","ʿaynin","āniyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1090],[3,1090,2070],[4,2070,3715]]}},{"name":"88:6","price":"उनके लिए कांटेदार झाड़ के सिवा कोई खाना नहीं होगा।","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahum ṭaʿāmun illā min ḍarīʿin ","translations":["Not is","for them","food","except","from","a bitter thorny plant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahum","ṭaʿāmun","illā","min","ḍarīʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1200],[3,1200,2250],[4,2250,3180],[5,3180,4510],[6,4510,7285]]}},{"name":"88:7","price":"जो न मोटा करेगा और न भूख मिटाएगा।[1]","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-7) इन आयतों में सबसे पहले सांसारिक स्वार्थ में मग्न इनसानों को एक प्रश्न द्वारा सावधान किया गया है कि उसे उस समय की सूचना है जब एक आपदा समस्त संसार पर छा जाएगी? फिर इसी के साथ यह विवरण भी दिया गया है कि उस समय इनसानों के दो भेद हो जाएँगे, और दोनों के प्रतिफल भी भिन्न होंगे : एक नरक में तथा दूसरा स्वर्ग में जाएगा। तीसरी आयत में \"नासिबह\" का शब्द आया है जिसका अर्थ है, थक कर चूर हो जाना, अर्थात काफ़िरों को क़ियामत के दिन इतनी कड़ी यातना दी जाएगी कि उनकी दशा बहुत ख़राब हो जाएगी। और वे थके-थके से दिखाई देंगे। इसका दूसरा अर्थ यह भी है कि उन्होंने संसार में बहुत-से कर्म किए होंगे, परंतु वे सत्य धर्म के अनुसार नहीं होंगे, इसलिए वे उपासना और कड़ी तपस्या करके भी नरक में जाएँगे। क्योंकि सत्य आस्था के बिना कोई कर्म मान्य नहीं होगा।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yus'minu walā yugh'nī min jūʿin ","translations":["Not","it nourishes","and not","it avails","from","hunger","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yus'minu","walā","yugh'nī","min","jūʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1330],[3,1330,1860],[4,1860,2750],[5,2750,3090],[6,3090,6355]]}},{"name":"88:8","price":"उस दिन कई चेहरे प्रफुल्लित होंगे।","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāʿimatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) joyful","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāʿimatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2430],[3,2430,5635]]}},{"name":"88:9","price":"अपने प्रयास पर प्रसन्न होंगे।","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lisaʿyihā rāḍiyatun ","translations":["With their effort","satisfied","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["lisaʿyihā","rāḍiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2965]]}},{"name":"88:10","price":"ऊँची जन्नत में होंगे।","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jannatin ʿāliyatin ","translations":["In","a garden","elevated","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jannatin","ʿāliyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2200],[3,2200,3725]]}},{"name":"88:11","price":"उसमें कोई बेकार (अशिष्ट) बात नहीं सुनेंगे।","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tasmaʿu fīhā lāghiyatan ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","vain talk","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tasmaʿu","fīhā","lāghiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1330],[3,1330,2280],[4,2280,3975]]}},{"name":"88:12","price":"उसमें बहने वाले स्रोत (चश्मे) हैं।","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā ʿaynun jāriyatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) a spring","flowing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","ʿaynun","jāriyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,2400],[3,2400,4174]]}},{"name":"88:13","price":"उसमें ऊँचे-ऊँचे तख्त हैं।","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā sururun marfūʿatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) thrones","raised high","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","sururun","marfūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1540],[3,1540,4315]]}},{"name":"88:14","price":"और (पीने वालों के लिए तैयार) रखे हुए प्याले हैं।","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akwābun mawḍūʿatun ","translations":["And cups","put in place","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akwābun","mawḍūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4005]]}},{"name":"88:15","price":"और क्रम में लगे हुए गाव-तकिए हैं।","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wanamāriqu maṣfūfatun ","translations":["And cushions","lined up","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wanamāriqu","maṣfūfatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3005]]}},{"name":"88:16","price":"और बिछाए हुए क़ालीन हैं।[2]","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (8-16) इन आयतों में जो इस संसार में सत्य आस्था के साथ क़ुरआन आदेशानुसार जीवन व्यतीत कर रहे हैं परलोक में उनके सदा के सुख का दृश्य दिखाया गया है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wazarābiyyu mabthūthatun ","translations":["And carpets","spread out","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wazarābiyyu","mabthūthatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,3475]]}},{"name":"88:17","price":"क्या वे ऊँटों को नहीं देखते कि वे कैसे पैदा किए गए हैं?","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yanẓurūna ilā al-ibili kayfa khuliqat ","translations":["Then do not","they look","towards","the camels","how","they are created","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yanẓurūna","ilā","al-ibili","kayfa","khuliqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,3130],[4,3130,4050],[5,4050,4670],[6,4670,5995]]}},{"name":"88:18","price":"और आकाश को (नहीं देखते) कि उसे कैसे ऊँचा किया गया?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-samāi kayfa rufiʿat ","translations":["And towards","the sky","how","it is raised","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-samāi","kayfa","rufiʿat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,3240],[3,3240,3810],[4,3810,5175]]}},{"name":"88:19","price":"और पर्वतों को (नहीं देखते) कि कैसे गाड़े गए हैं?","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-jibāli kayfa nuṣibat ","translations":["And towards","the mountains","how","they are fixed","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-jibāli","kayfa","nuṣibat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,1720],[3,1720,2330],[4,2330,3585]]}},{"name":"88:20","price":"तथा धरती को (नहीं देखते) कि कैसे बिछाई गई है?[3]","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (17-20) इन आयतों में फिर विषय बदल कर एक प्रश्न किया जा रहा है कि जो क़ुरआन की शिक्षा तथा परलोक की सूचना को नहीं मानते, अपने सामने उन चीज़ों को नहीं देखते जो रात दिन उनके सामने आती रहती हैं, ऊँटों तथा पर्वतों और आकाश एवं धरती पर विचार क्यों नहीं करते कि क्या ये सब अपने आप पैदा हो गए हैं या इनका कोई रचयिता है? यह तो असंभव है कि रचना हो और रचयिता न हो। यदि मानते हैं कि किसी शक्ति ने इनको बनाया है जिसका कोई साझी नहीं तो उसके अकेले पूज्य होने और उसके फिर से पैदा करने की शक्ति और सामर्थ्य का क्यों इनकार करते हैं? (तर्जुमानुल क़ुरआन)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-arḍi kayfa suṭiḥat ","translations":["And towards","the earth","how","it is spread out","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-arḍi","kayfa","suṭiḥat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1530],[3,1530,2070],[4,2070,3375]]}},{"name":"88:21","price":"अतः आप नसीहत करें, आप केवल नसीहत करने वाले हैं।","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir innamā anta mudhakkirun ","translations":["So remind","only","you","(are) a reminder","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","innamā","anta","mudhakkirun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,4020],[3,4020,5240],[4,5240,6615]]}},{"name":"88:22","price":"आप उनपर कोई दरोग़ा (नियंत्रक) नहीं हैं।","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"lasta ʿalayhim bimuṣayṭirin ","translations":["You are not","over them","a controller","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["lasta","ʿalayhim","bimuṣayṭirin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2310],[3,2310,3945]]}},{"name":"88:23","price":"परंतु जिसने मुँह फेरा और कुफ़्र किया।","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"illā man tawallā wakafara ","translations":["But","whoever","turns away","and disbelieves","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","man","tawallā","wakafara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1890],[3,1890,3020],[4,3020,4295]]}},{"name":"88:24","price":"तो अल्लाह उसे सबसे बड़ी यातना देगा।","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fayuʿadhibuhu al-lahu al-ʿadhāba al-akbara ","translations":["Then will punish him","Allah","(with) the punishment","greatest","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["fayuʿadhibuhu","al-lahu","al-ʿadhāba","al-akbara",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,2280],[3,2280,3350],[4,3350,4975]]}},{"name":"88:25","price":"निःसंदेह हमारी ही ओर उनका लौटकर आना है।","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ilaynā iyābahum ","translations":["Indeed","to Us","(will be) their return","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ilaynā","iyābahum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1380],[2,1380,3820],[3,3820,5625]]}},{"name":"88:26","price":"फिर बेशक हमारे ही ज़िम्मे उनका ह़िसाब लेना है।[4]","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4. (21-26) इन आयतों का भावार्थ यह है कि क़ुरआन किसी को बलपूर्वक मनवाने के लिए नहीं है, और न नबी सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम 